devdoc.details: Token router to liquidity to the Uniswap V3 pool in exchange for an LP NFT

IncentiveCreated(address,uint256,uint256.details: Emitted when a new incentive is created

params.creator: The address of the creator
params.endTime: The end time of the incentive
params.startTime: The start time of the incentive

NFTStaked(address,address,address,uint25.details: Emitted when a Uniswap V3 LP NFT is staked

params.baseTokenAmount: The amount of base tokens spent on the NFT
params.nftAddress: The address of the NFT manager contract
params.recipient: The address of the recipient of the LP NFT
params.sender: The sender of the underlying stablecoins
params.stableAmounts: The amounts of stablecoins spent on the NFT                      (0 = DAI, 1 = USDC, 2 = USDT)

NFTUnstaked(address,address,address,uint.details: Emitted when a Uniswap V3 LP NFT is unstaked

params.nftAddress: The address of the NFT manager contract
params.rewardClaimed: The amount of the base token claimed as a reward for                      staking the LP NFT
params.stableIndex: The index of the stablecoin to receive                    (0 = DAI, 1 = USDC, 2 = USDT)
params.stablesReturned: The amount of stablecoins returned to the recipient

params.lpSft_: The address of the LP SFT contract
params.owner_: The initial owner of the contract
params.uniV3Pooler_: The address of our Uniswap V3 pooler contract
params.uniswapV3Staker_: The address of the Uniswap V3 staker contract

params.reward: The reward to distribute in the incentive TODO: Allow creating multiple incentives?

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby disabling any functionality that is only available to the owner.

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

baseIsToken0.details: If true, the base token is token0 and the asset token is token1, otherwise the reverse

incentiveCreated.details: True if the incentive has been created, false otherwise

incentiveId.details: The Uniswap V3 staker incentive ID, calculated when the incentive is created

incentiveKey.details: The Uniswap V3 staker incentive key, calculated when the incentive is created

uniswapV3NftManager.details: The upstream Uniswap V3 NFT manager

uniswapV3Pool.details: The upstream Uniswap V3 pool for the token pair

uniswapV3Staker.details: The upstream Uniswap V3 NFT staker
